# Rung 5 slice E restore receipt: run AFTER rung5_workbench.scn on the SAME
# profile (the harness's -Root). A fresh process finds the stacked workbench
# back off workbench.json — platen's canonical (Arrangement, geometry) pair,
# pruned to the restored graph's members.
settle 30
key escape
assert pane workbench
assert wb-cells == 1
assert wb-cell Example Domain
assert wb-cell Internet
capture 01_restored
log workbench restore receipt complete
